import React from 'react'
import {Card,Form,Button,Col, Row, Container} from "react-bootstrap"
import Profile from './Profile'
import Tweets from './Tweets'


export default class HomePage extends React.Component {

    render() {

        return(
            <>
            <Row>
                <Col>
                    <Container>
                        <Profile/>
                    </Container>
                    </Col>
                <Col>
                Twitterfeed
                    <Container>
                        <Tweets/>
                    </Container>
                    </Col>
            </Row>
            </>
        )
    }
}
